column16: Chase Utley doubles (20) on a fly ball to left fielder Roger Bernadina, deflected by center fielder Nyjer Morgan.    Shane Victorino scores.    Placido Polanco scores.
Placido Polanco singles on a line drive to center fielder Nyjer Morgan.    Wilson Valdez scores.    Shane Victorino to 3rd.
Roy Halladay strikes out swinging.  Wilson Valdez steals (6) 2nd base.
Wilson Valdez strikes out swinging, catcher Wilson Ramos to third baseman Alberto Gonzalez.    Wilson Valdez to 1st.
Carlos Ruiz doubles (27) on a sharp line drive to center fielder Nyjer Morgan.
Melky Cabrera called out on strikes.
Nate McLouth walks.    Freddie Freeman to 2nd.
Carlos Lee grounds into double play, shortstop Danny Espinosa to second baseman Adam Kennedy to first baseman Adam Dunn.    Hunter Pence out at 2nd.
Hunter Pence singles on a ground ball to center fielder Roger Bernadina.    Jeff Keppinger to 2nd.
Jason Bourgeois lines out to center fielder Roger Bernadina.
Placido Polanco flies out to right fielder Willie Harris.
Greg Dobbs pops out to shortstop Ian Desmond.
Wilson Valdez lines out to right fielder Willie Harris.
Carlos Ruiz homers (8) on a fly ball to left field.   Raul Ibanez scores.
Raul Ibanez reaches on missed catch error by pitcher Joe Bisenius, assist to first baseman Adam Dunn.
Chad Tracy pops out to third baseman Ryan Zimmerman.
Brad Davis singles on a line drive to center fielder Nyjer Morgan.
Cameron Maybin grounds out, third baseman Ryan Zimmerman to first baseman Adam Dunn.
Mike Stanton flies out to center fielder Nyjer Morgan.
